3.1.1
    * check if queue changed status following Switcher decision, with WARNING message in the email in case it did not
3.1.0
    * email notifications to the clouds with content for a single Site per message
    * checking explicitly that SRM or SRMv2 are in the "affected_serviced" field in downtimes data, to prevent blacklisting tape-only queues
    * trying 3 attempts reading input data before giving up
    * new class SwitcherLoop where the main loop is coded, instead of Switcher.run()
    * new Exceptions to be raised when data can not be read
    * not shuttingdown the service if input data can not be read, just wait to next cycle
